{"tid":772683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港只要經濟好大家搵到錢 咩政治環境變成點都唔關你事啦😂","createTime":"2018-08-09T03:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T05:58:48.000Z","uid":20241,"like":20,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd098d2dd86eada894bba79000c7af016fa88af","tid":772683,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"我同我啲同事傾過<br />\n大家都係諗住兩公婆係度搏廿年搵到舊錢之後<br />\n個仔女升大個時<br />\n有料就過美加<br />\n無料就移民台灣<br />\n個邊買間屋舒舒服服享受人生 剩低既錢搞下小生意 香港呢邊就買下收息既股債咁<br />\n根本香港變成點多唔多支那人南亞人對我地黎講都係wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真個啲大大聲話有感情咩住慣左個班友<br />\n講到尾咪又係冇錢/冇料移民<br />\n有錢有能力你估佢地走唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0d05388a1d1d2fb5830f1be5a4b6346261e1b7","tid":772683,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:25:20.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀"},{"pid":"8309c21ace6e0665db7777bd4eab869829fb8efe","tid":772683,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"根本啲有料鬼佬都係 邊度搵到食 帶住全家去個邊<br />\n最後退休咪搵個自己鐘意既國家養老<br />\n係啲小農基因先會諗咩生於斯長於斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafd379ac7769682a8c46cbd5ccf3ca45a5987cb","tid":772683,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8309c21ace6e0665db7777bd4eab869829fb8efe","tid":772683,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"根本啲有料鬼佬都係 邊度搵到食 帶住全家去個邊<br />\n最後退休咪搵個自己鐘意既國家養老<br />\n係啲小農基因先會諗咩生於斯長於斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話自己係香港人唔係中國人，根本個種一樣諗野都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ad41fad77d5da6